6-03-05 22:24:30','2026-03-05 22:24:30','A stunning 1960s Omega manual-wind dress watch with a silver dial featuring beautifully faceted diamond-shaped hour markers that catch the light wonderfully. The elegant leaf-style hands sweep across the clean dial, which bears only the Omega logo and Swiss Made text — the epitome of understated sophistication. The stainless steel case has a smooth bezel and well-proportioned lugs. Presented on a black leather strap. The caseback is plain polished stainless steel. This is the kind of watch that looks equally at home with a suit or a casual weekend outfit. A true gentleman\'s timepiece from Omega\'s golden era.','Omega Dress Watch — 1960s Manual Wind','1960s Omega manual-wind dress watch with silver dial, faceted diamond hour markers, on black leather strap.','publish','open','closed','','omega-dress-watch-1960s-manual-wind','','','2026-03-05 22:24:30','2026-03-05 22:24:30','',0,'http://localhost:8080/product/omega-dress-watch-1960s-manual-wind/',0,'product','',0),(94,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:31','2026-03-05 22:24:31','','Omega Dress Watch — 1960s Manual Wind - Dial','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-dress-watch-1960s-manual-wind-dial','','','2026-03-05 22:24:31','2026-03-05 22:24:31','',93,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-34.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(95,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:34','2026-03-05 22:24:34','','Omega Dress Watch — 1960s Manual Wind - Caseback','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-dress-watch-1960s-manual-wind-caseback','','','2026-03-05 22:24:34','2026-03-05 22:24:34','',93,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-35.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(96,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:36','2026-03-05 22:24:36','','Omega Dress Watch — 1960s Manual Wind - Side Profile','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-dress-watch-1960s-manual-wind-side-profile','','','2026-03-05 22:24:36','2026-03-05 22:24:36','',93,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-36.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(97,1,'2026-03-05 22:24:39','2026-03-05 22:24:39','A handsome 1960s Omega Seamaster Automatic with a cream/ivory dial featuring warm gold-tone applied baton indices and matching gold dauphine hands. The Seamaster script and Omega Automatic text add vintage charm, while the date window at 6 o\'clock provides everyday practicality. The stainless steel case is well-proportioned with the Seamaster Waterproof caseback featuring the iconic hippocampus (sea monster) medallion. Presented on a black leather strap. This watch has the warm, lived-in patina that vintage watch collectors prize. Runs well and keeps good time.','Omega Seamaster Automatic — 1960s with Date','1960s Omega Seamaster Automatic with cream dial, gold indices, date, and Seamaster caseback.','publish','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-automatic-1960s-with-date','','','2026-03-05 22:24:39','2026-03-05 22:24:39','',0,'http://localhost:8080/product/omega-seamaster-automatic-1960s-with-date/',0,'product','',0),(98,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:40','2026-03-05 22:24:40','','Omega Seamaster Automatic — 1960s with Date - Dial','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-automatic-1960s-with-date-dial','','','2026-03-05 22:24:40','2026-03-05 22:24:40','',97,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-37.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(99,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:43','2026-03-05 22:24:43','','Omega Seamaster Automatic — 1960s with Date - Caseback','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-automatic-1960s-with-date-caseback','','','2026-03-05 22:24:43','2026-03-05 22:24:43','',97,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-38.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(100,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:45','2026-03-05 22:24:45','','Omega Seamaster Automatic — 1960s with Date - Side Profile','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-automatic-1960s-with-date-side-profile','','','2026-03-05 22:24:45','2026-03-05 22:24:45','',97,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-39.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(101,1,'2026-03-05 22:24:48','2026-03-05 22:24:48','A refined Omega Seamaster De Ville Automatic from the 1960s with a clean silver sunburst dial. Applied black baton indices with luminous plots and polished silver hands create excellent legibility. The Seamaster De Ville script alongside the Omega Automatic text gives this watch its proper identity, and the date window at 6 o\'clock adds utility. The Seamaster Waterproof caseback with hippocampus medallion is crisp and well-defined. Presented on a black crocodile-pattern leather strap with contrast white stitching. A versatile and elegant vintage piece that transitions effortlessly from office to evening.','Omega Seamaster De Ville Automatic — Silver Dial','Omega Seamaster De Ville Automatic with silver dial, date, and black croc strap.','publish','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-de-ville-automatic-silver-dial','','','2026-03-05 22:24:48','2026-03-05 22:24:48','',0,'http://localhost:8080/product/omega-seamaster-de-ville-automatic-silver-dial/',0,'product','',0),(102,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:49','2026-03-05 22:24:49','','Omega Seamaster De Ville Automatic — Silver Dial - Dial','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-de-ville-automatic-silver-dial-dial','','','2026-03-05 22:24:49','2026-03-05 22:24:49','',101,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-40.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(103,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:52','2026-03-05 22:24:52','','Omega Seamaster De Ville Automatic — Silver Dial - Caseback','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-de-ville-automatic-silver-dial-caseback','','','2026-03-05 22:24:52','2026-03-05 22:24:52','',101,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-41.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(104,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:54','2026-03-05 22:24:54','','Omega Seamaster De Ville Automatic — Silver Dial - Side Profile','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-de-ville-automatic-silver-dial-side-profile','','','2026-03-05 22:24:54','2026-03-05 22:24:54','',101,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-42.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(105,1,'2026-03-05 22:24:57','2026-03-05 22:24:57','A prized 1960s Omega Constellation Automatic Chronometer — the flagship of Omega\'s range during this era. The silver dial features applied baton indices, the iconic Constellation star at 6 o\'clock, and the text \'Automatic / Chronometer / Officially Certified\'. The date window sits at the 3 o\'clock position. The caseback features the famous Observatory medallion with eight stars, representing Omega\'s record-breaking chronometer testing achievements. Presented on a black leather strap. The Constellation was Omega\'s answer to Rolex\'s Datejust — a premium, COSC-certified daily wear watch. This example has wonderful vintage character.','Omega Constellation Automatic Chronometer — 1960s','1960s Omega Constellation Automatic Chronometer with silver dial, star emblem, and Observatory caseback.','publish','open','closed','','omega-constellation-automatic-chronometer-1960s','','','2026-03-05 22:24:57','2026-03-05 22:24:57','',0,'http://localhost:8080/product/omega-constellation-automatic-chronometer-1960s/',0,'product','',0),(106,0,'2026-03-05 22:24:58','2026-03-05 22:24:58','','Omega Constellation Automatic Chronometer — 1960s - Dial','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-constellation-automatic-chronometer-1960s-dial','','','2026-03-05 22:24:58','2026-03-05 22:24:58','',105,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-43.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(107,0,'2026-03-05 22:25:01','2026-03-05 22:25:01','','Omega Constellation Automatic Chronometer — 1960s - Caseback','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-constellation-automatic-chronometer-1960s-caseback','','','2026-03-05 22:25:01','2026-03-05 22:25:01','',105,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-44.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(108,0,'2026-03-05 22:25:03','2026-03-05 22:25:03','','Omega Constellation Automatic Chronometer — 1960s - Side Profile','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-constellation-automatic-chronometer-1960s-side-profile','','','2026-03-05 22:25:03','2026-03-05 22:25:03','',105,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-45.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(109,1,'2026-03-05 22:25:06','2026-03-05 22:25:06','An Omega Seamaster Cosmic from the late 1960s/early 1970s, reference 136022. The silver dial with black baton indices and a crosshair pattern creates a sporty yet refined look. The date window at 6 o\'clock adds functionality. The Seamaster Cosmic was positioned as a younger, sportier alternative to the standard Seamaster range. The Seamaster caseback features the Waterproof engraving and hippocampus medallion, with reference 136022 and Tool 107 clearly visible. Presented on a black leather strap. The manual-wind movement is reliable and easy to service. A cool, affordable entry point to vintage Omega collecting.','Omega Seamaster Cosmic — Ref. 136022','Omega Seamaster Cosmic Ref. 136022 with silver dial, date, and Seamaster caseback.','publish','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-cosmic-ref-136022','','','2026-03-05 22:25:06','2026-03-05 22:25:06','',0,'http://localhost:8080/product/omega-seamaster-cosmic-ref-136022/',0,'product','',0),(110,0,'2026-03-05 22:25:07','2026-03-05 22:25:07','','Omega Seamaster Cosmic — Ref. 136022 - Dial','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-cosmic-ref-136022-dial','','','2026-03-05 22:25:07','2026-03-05 22:25:07','',109,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-46.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(111,0,'2026-03-05 22:25:10','2026-03-05 22:25:10','','Omega Seamaster Cosmic — Ref. 136022 - Caseback','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-cosmic-ref-136022-caseback','','','2026-03-05 22:25:10','2026-03-05 22:25:10','',109,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-47.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(112,0,'2026-03-05 22:25:12','2026-03-05 22:25:12','','Omega Seamaster Cosmic — Ref. 136022 - Side Profile','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-seamaster-cosmic-ref-136022-side-profile','','','2026-03-05 22:25:12','2026-03-05 22:25:12','',109,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-48.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(113,1,'2026-03-05 22:25:15','2026-03-05 22:25:15','A sleek Omega De Ville with a distinctive rectangular tank-style case in stainless steel. The silver-grey dial features minimal indices — just four thin baton markers — and the De Ville / Omega branding, creating an extremely clean, modern aesthetic that belies its vintage origins. The slim case profile and elegant proportions make this watch sit beautifully on the wrist. Presented on a black lizard-skin strap. The caseback is solid stainless steel. Tank and rectangular watches have seen a resurgence in popularity, and this piece offers genuine vintage Swiss quality at a fraction of the price of a Cartier Tank. A true connoisseur\'s choice.','Omega De Ville — Rectangular Tank Case','Omega De Ville rectangular tank case with silver dial on black lizard strap.','publish','open','closed','','omega-de-ville-rectangular-tank-case','','','2026-03-05 22:25:15','2026-03-05 22:25:15','',0,'http://localhost:8080/product/omega-de-ville-rectangular-tank-case/',0,'product','',0),(114,0,'2026-03-05 22:25:16','2026-03-05 22:25:16','','Omega De Ville — Rectangular Tank Case - Dial','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-de-ville-rectangular-tank-case-dial','','','2026-03-05 22:25:16','2026-03-05 22:25:16','',113,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-49.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(115,0,'2026-03-05 22:25:19','2026-03-05 22:25:19','','Omega De Ville — Rectangular Tank Case - Caseback','','inherit','open','closed','','omega-de-ville-rectangular-tank-case-caseback','','','2026-03-05 22:25:19','2026-03-05 22:25:19','',113,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/S-50.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(116,0,'2026-03-05 22:48:16',