26-03-05 23:17:39','','The Watch Locator Logo','','inherit','open','closed','','the-watch-locator-logo','','','2026-03-05 23:17:39','2026-03-05 23:17:39','',0,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/twl-logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(118,1,'2026-03-05 23:24:15','2026-03-05 23:24:15','','Order &ndash; March 5, 2026 @ 11:24 PM','','wc-checkout-draft','open','closed','wc_order_PLUrfVBUXY279','order-mar-05-2026-1124-pm','','','2026-03-05 23:24:15','2026-03-05 23:24:15','',0,'http://localhost:8080/?post_type=shop_order&p=118',0,'shop_order','',0),(119,0,'2026-03-06 19:54:07','2026-03-06 19:54:07','<div class=\"twl-page-section\">\n    <h2 class=\"twl-section-heading\">Our Story</h2>\n    <div class=\"twl-prose\">\n        <p>The Watch Locator was founded with a singular vision: to connect discerning collectors with the world\'s most exceptional timepieces. What began as a passion for horology has grown into one of the UK\'s most trusted names in luxury watch sourcing and authentication.</p>\n        <p>With over two decades of experience in the luxury watch market, our team of certified horologists and watch specialists has built an unrivalled network of trusted dealers, collectors, and auction houses across the globe. We leverage these relationships to source timepieces that meet our exacting standards of quality and authenticity.</p>\n        <p>Every watch that passes through our hands undergoes a rigorous multi-point inspection process, ensuring that each piece meets the highest standards before reaching its new owner. Our commitment to transparency and integrity has earned us the trust of collectors worldwide.</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"twl-page-section-gray\">\n    <h2 class=\"twl-section-heading twl-section-heading-centered\">Our Expertise</h2>\n    <div class=\"twl-features\">\n        <div class=\"twl-feature\">\n            <div class=\"twl-feature-icon\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" 