.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"twl-feature\">\n            <div class=\"twl-feature-icon\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"m21 21-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 1 0 5.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 10.607 10.607Z\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Thorough Authentication</h3>\n            <p>Every timepiece undergoes a comprehensive multi-point inspection including movement analysis, case verification, and provenance review.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"twl-image-banner\">\n    <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/hero-watch.jpg\" alt=\"The Watch Locator showroom — luxury watches on display\" />\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"twl-page-section\">\n    <h2 class=\"twl-section-heading twl-section-heading-centered\">Why Choose Us</h2>\n    <div class=\"twl-info-grid\">\n        <div class=\"twl-info-card\">\n            <div class=\"twl-info-card-icon\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Authentication Guarantee</h3>\n            <p>Every watch comes with our certificate of authenticity, backed by our team of certified horologists and industry-leading inspection process.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"twl-info-card\">\n            <div class=\"twl-info-card-icon\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Competitive Pricing</h3>\n            <p>Our extensive network and industry relationships allow us to offer exceptional timepieces at competitive prices, ensuring outstanding value for collectors.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"twl-info-card\">\n            <div class=\"twl-info-card-icon\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3>Trusted by Collectors</h3>\n            <p>Join thousands of satisfied collectors who have trusted The Watch Locator to source and authenticate their most prized timepieces.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n','About','','inhe